{"tid":1461593,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"勇者鬥惡龍，勇者變惡龍","createTime":"2019-08-13T08:32:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T09:43:32.000Z","uid":240862,"like":8,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ee0888c509b703ec78af4b3b6eb18119dda069c5","tid":1461593,"uid":240862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T08:32:59.000Z","msg":"見好多人講話要麻包袋d POPO, 又要禍及妻兒, 我想講既係希望各位手足唔好令到自已由勇者變惡龍，成為自己最討厭既惡龍。<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">行私刑既勇者唔會再係勇者</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。我知道好多人都好嬲，好多人受到濫暴既警察傷害，又有好多人想幫個女仔討番個公道。<br />\n但係拎住大義更加要行正道，否則只會成為你最討厭既人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/battle.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：放核彈都唔割。<br />\n<br />\n懇請不要被仇恨支配自已，在危難中，仍要保持警覺與思考。( 梁天琦，2019)<br />\n<br />\n在實現民主前，也許我們必先實踐民主，理解各種分歧，珍惜彼此的差異，並以此為凝聚更大力量的契機，只有獨裁才容不下其他的聲音。(梁天琦，2018)<br />\n<br />\n天佑吾城。"},{"pid":"ca18dbfb48d506a56e173b547ae02d3fb608ab6b","tid":1461593,"uid":115133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T08:33:42.000Z","msg":"全民親善大使月 正式啟動！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1461455\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1461455</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n求建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dd2e5903c3fb4fc1d0816f0a6cfbd9da94dd457","tid":1461593,"uid":240862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca18dbfb48d506a56e173b547ae02d3fb608ab6b","tid":1461593,"uid":115133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T08:33:42.000Z","msg":"全民親善大使月 正式啟動！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1461455\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1461455</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n求建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T08:36:24.000Z","msg":"睇下先，一路番工心情都好差<img src=\"